  <refsection xml:id="sources.openssl.doc.crypto.RSA_size.pod:HISTORY"><title>HISTORY</title>
    <para>
      RSA_size() is available in all versions of SSLeay and OpenSSL.
      RSA_bits() was added in OpenSSL 1.1.0.
